To use the video capture first create a named pipe:

> mkfifo npipe

In a separate shell but in the same directory start the video processing script

> python videocapture.py

And then run a ffmpeg command grabbing the video from anywhere.

> ffmpeg -probesize 4k -re -y -i <source> -s 320x240 -an -vcodec mjpeg -qscale 2 -f avi npipe
